text: Carolina Aguirre (born 29 January 1996) is a female Colombian recurve archer from Antioquia Department.http://www.elmundo.com/portal/pagina.general.impresion.php?idx=262165 She competed in the archery competition at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, finishing in 52nd place in the recurve event. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Colombian female archers Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:1996 births Category:Archers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic archers of Colombia
